{"type":"message","id":"b06d55e8","parentId":"13b692f2","timestamp":"2026-04-04T02:31:36.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill has been installed successfully. The skill has hooks set up in the hooks/ directory. Let me check if the user wants me to enable the hooks. Based on the skill description, the optional hook setup would enable automatic reminders at session start.\n\nLet me ask if they want me to enable the hooks as well. Actually, looking at the instructions again:\n\n\"Optional: Enable Hook\nFor automatic reminders at session start:\n# Copy hook to OpenClaw hooks directory\ncp -r hooks/openclaw ~/.openclaw/hooks/self-improvement\n\n# Enable it\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\"\n\nI should ask if they want this enabled, but actually since they asked me to \"安装这个技能\" (install this skill), maybe they just want the basic install done. Let me provide a summary of what was done and mention the hooks as optional.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **self-improving-agent v3.0.13 安装完成！**\n\n已安装到：`/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving-agent`\n\n初始化了学习文件：\n- `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` - 记录学习内容、纠正、知识盲点\n- `.learnings/ERRORS.md` - 记录命令失败和错误\n- `.learnings/FEATURE_REQUESTS.md` - 记录功能请求\n\n这个技能会自动在以下情况提醒我记录学习：\n- 命令/操作失败时 → 记录到 ERRORS.md\n- 你纠正我时 → 记录到 LEARNINGS.md\n- 我发现更好的方法时 → 记录为 best_practice\n- 你请求新功能时 → 记录到 FEATURE_REQUESTS.md\n\n如果你想启用自动提醒钩子（可选），可以运行：\n```bash\ncp -r ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/self-improving-agent/hooks/openclaw ~/.openclaw/hooks/self-improvement\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\n```\n\n需要帮你启用钩子吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":617,"output":397,"cacheRead":20352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775269867719,"responseId":"019d565469860ecfce109401f1cf9a1d"}}
