{"type":"message","id":"cd6b2402","parentId":"be8460bb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:14:30.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what these three newly installed skills do and how to use them. Let me summarize:\n\n1. **self-improving-agent** (v3.0.13) - .learnings/ based\n2. **self-improving** (v1.2.16) - ~/self-improving/ based\n3. **proactivity** - ~/proactivity/ based\n4. **ontology** (v1.0.4) - knowledge graph\n\nActually wait, the user said \"这三个技能\" - which three? They installed:\n1. self-improving-agent\n2. self-improving + proactivity\n3. ontology\n\nActually, self-improving and proactivity were installed together as a set. So the three could be:\n- self-improving-agent\n- self-improving\n- proactivity\n\nOr maybe they mean the most recent three: self-improving, proactivity, and ontology.\n\nLet me explain all of them clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n今天安装了 4 个技能，让我帮你梳理：\n\n---\n\n## 1. self-improving-agent (v3.0.13)\n**用途**：结构化记录学习、错误、特性请求  \n**存储**：`.learnings/` 目录\n\n| 触发场景 | 记录位置 |\n|---------|---------|\n| 命令失败 | `.learnings/ERRORS.md` |\n| 你纠正我 | `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` |\n| 请求新功能 | `.learnings/FEATURE_REQUESTS.md` |\n\n**用法**：我自动记录，无需你操作\n\n---\n\n## 2. self-improving (v1.2.16)\n**用途**：分层记忆系统，记住你的偏好和工作模式  \n**存储**：`~/self-improving/`\n\n| 层级 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| HOT (memory.md) | 始终加载，常用规则 |\n| WARM (domains/, projects/) | 按需加载 |\n| COLD (archive/) | 归档模式 |\n\n**用法**：\n- 告诉我 \"记住我更喜欢简洁的回答\" → 写入 memory.md\n- 重复纠正 3 次 → 自动提升为 HOT 规则\n\n---\n\n## 3. proactivity\n**用途**：主动做事，不等你问  \n**存储**：`~/proactivity/`\n\n**我會主动做：**\n- 注意到缺失的下一步 → 提醒你\n- 工作卡住了 → 尝试不同方法\n- 完成后 → 验证结果而不是假定成功\n\n---\n\n## 4. ontology (v1.0.4)\n**用途**：结构化知识图谱  \n**存储**：`memory/ontology/graph.jsonl`\n\n**用法**（需要时叫我）：\n- \"记住 Alice 在做 X 项目\" → 创建 Project 实体 + Person 关联\n- \"显示所有待办任务\" → 查询 Task 实体\n- \"X 依赖于 Y 吗？\" → 图遍历查询\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n| 技能 | 核心能力 |\n|------|---------|\n| self-improving-agent | 错误日志 + 结构化学习 |\n| self-improving | 长期偏好记忆 |\n| proactivity | 主动跟进 + 防止遗漏 |\n| ontology | 知识图谱 + 关系查询 |\n\n我现在已经加载了这些技能的使用方式。有什么需要我记录或查询的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2661,"output":678,"cacheRead":44416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775272435406,"responseId":"019d567b9909cc79bab6713f77144109"}}
