{"type":"message","id":"ec8e9fdc","parentId":"a7f3bb4b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:23:18.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有技能都安装成功了。让我给用户一个总结。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **第一 + 第二梯队全部安装完成！**\n\n| 技能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| elite-longterm-memory | ✅ |\n| automation-workflows | ✅ |\n| openclaw-github-assistant | ✅ |\n| agent-team-orchestration | ✅ |\n| productivity-automation-kit | ✅ |\n| clawdbot-filesystem | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**当前已安装技能汇总 (10个)：**\n\n1. self-improving-agent — 错误/学习日志\n2. self-improving — 分层记忆\n3. proactivity — 主动行为\n4. ontology — 知识图谱\n5. **elite-longterm-memory** — 增强长期记忆 ⭐\n6. **automation-workflows** — 自动化工作流 ⭐\n7. **openclaw-github-assistant** — GitHub 助手 ⭐\n8. **agent-team-orchestration** — 多智能体编排 ⭐\n9. **productivity-automation-kit** — 生产力自动化 ⭐\n10. **clawdbot-filesystem** — 文件系统增强 ⭐\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你配置其中某个技能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":53155,"output":248,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53403,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775272993520,"responseId":"chatcmpl-713440b8-2c0f-4845-8485-def19f984ee2"}}
