{"type":"message","id":"ec0741f2","parentId":"eb63455f","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:25:36.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All configured. Now let me summarize everything for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **全部配置完成！**\n\n| 技能 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **automation-workflows** | ✅ | 自动化工作流指南 ( playbook ) |\n| **agent-team-orchestration** | ✅ | 多智能体编排指南 ( playbook ) |\n| **productivity-automation-kit** | ✅ | 效率自动化工具箱 ( playbook ) |\n| **clawdbot-filesystem** | ✅ | 文件系统增强 (自动生效) |\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | ✅ | 已启用 memory-lancedb 插件 |\n| **openclaw-github-assistant** | ⚠️ | **需要 GitHub Token** |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 GitHub 助手配置\n\n需要你提供以下信息来启用 GitHub 功能：\n\n1. **GitHub Token** — [生成地址](https://github.com/settings/tokens)\n   - 勾选 `repo` 权限 (私有仓库) 或 `public_repo` (仅公开仓库)\n   \n2. **GitHub 用户名** — 你的 GitHub 账号 ID\n\n**配置方式（选一个）：**\n\n**方式 A**：直接告诉我，我帮你写入配置\n```json\n\"github\": {\n  \"token\": \"ghp_你的token\",\n  \"username\": \"你的用户名\"\n}\n```\n\n**方式 B**：设置环境变量\n```bash\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=\"ghp_你的token\"\nexport GITHUB_USERNAME=\"你的用户名\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📦 当前全部技能 (13个)\n\n| 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| self-improving-agent | 错误/学习日志 |\n| self-improving | 分层记忆 |\n| proactivity | 主动行为 |\n| ontology | 知识图谱 |\n| elite-longterm-memory | 增强长期记忆 + LanceDB |\n| automation-workflows | 自动化工作流 |\n| openclaw-github-assistant | GitHub 操作 |\n| agent-team-orchestration | 多智能体编排 |\n| productivity-automation-kit | 效率自动化 |\n| clawdbot-filesystem | 文件系统增强 |\n\n需要我帮你配置 GitHub Token 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":401,"output":454,"cacheRead":61184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273117113,"responseId":"019d568566bc01fcbc285de25858f46c"}}
