{"type":"message","id":"7c8bd411","parentId":"925d3ea0","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:29:08.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The token works! I successfully fetched the user's repos. The GitHub configuration is complete.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **GitHub 配置完成！**\n\n| 配置项 | 值 |\n|--------|-----|\n| Token | `github_pat_11BEMPCWI0...` ✅ |\n| Username | `llwxw` ✅ |\n\n**验证成功**：获取到你的仓库 `llwxw/JMComic-Crawler-Python`\n\n---\n\n## 📋 全部配置总结\n\n| 技能 | 配置状态 |\n|------|---------|\n| self-improving-agent | ✅ 钩子已启用 |\n| self-improving | ✅ 已配置内存结构 |\n| proactivity | ✅ 已配置状态文件 |\n| ontology | ✅ 已修复 Python 兼容性 |\n| elite-longterm-memory | ✅ memory-lancedb 已启用 |\n| automation-workflows | ✅ playbook 已就绪 |\n| openclaw-github-assistant | ✅ Token + 用户名已配置 |\n| agent-team-orchestration | ✅ playbook 已就绪 |\n| productivity-automation-kit | ✅ 模板已就绪 |\n| clawdbot-filesystem | ✅ 自动生效 |\n\n---\n\n**技能使用方式**：\n- **Playbook 类** (automation-workflows, agent-team-orchestration 等): 触发相关话题时自动加载\n- **工具类** (filesystem, github): 直接呼叫\n- **记忆类** (self-improving, proactivity, elite-longterm-memory): 自动生效\n\n全部搞定！🎉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":402,"output":301,"cacheRead":62848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63551,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273334709,"responseId":"019d5688b836c460ec08c7330c0f4b7c"}}
