{"type":"message","id":"3b28d9e6","parentId":"b9131c52","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:31:10.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me provide a clearer analysis.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 🎯 技能冲突分析\n\n**结论：没有真正冲突，但有功能重叠**\n\n---\n\n### 记忆系统 (可能有轻微重叠)\n\n| 技能 | 存储位置 | 用途 | 重叠度 |\n|------|---------|------|--------|\n| self-improving-agent | `.learnings/` | 错误日志、纠正 | 低 |\n| self-improving | `~/self-improving/` | 偏好、模式、规则 | 中 |\n| proactivity | `~/proactivity/` | 主动状态、跟进 | 低 |\n| elite-longterm-memory | LanceDB | 向量语义记忆 | 高 |\n| ontology | `memory/ontology/` | 结构化实体/关系 | 低 |\n\n**实际运作方式：**\n- 它们各自负责不同场景，不会互相干扰\n- elite-longterm-memory 是增强版，会调用 LanceDB 向量搜索\n- 其他几个是互补的，不会同时触发\n\n---\n\n### 无冲突的技能\n\n| 组 | 技能 |\n|----|------|\n| **自动化** | automation-workflows, productivity-automation-kit |\n| **编排** | agent-team-orchestration |\n| **工具** | clawdbot-filesystem, openclaw-github-assistant |\n| **知识** | ontology |\n\n---\n\n### 为什么不会冲突？\n\n1. **触发条件不同** — 有的自动触发，有的需要特定关键词\n2. **写入目标不同** — 各自有独立的存储位置\n3. **职责不同** — 一个管记忆，一个管主动，一个管知识图谱\n\n---\n\n**如果你觉得记忆系统太多，可以考虑：**\n- 保留 `self-improving` + `proactivity` (简单够用)\n- 启用 `elite-longterm-memory` (增强搜索)\n\n但目前没有冲突风险，可以先用着再说 ✅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2794,"output":368,"cacheRead":61312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273438733,"responseId":"019d568ae8289788a96902cab30ff2de"}}
