{"type":"message","id":"80a291a5","parentId":"f502e85b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:39:19.369Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e37d4443a29345e793ce934d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                )}\r\n                {isYaml && (\r\n                  <YAMLEditor\r\n                    content={currentFile.content}\r\n                    onSave={handleSave}\r\n                    filePath={fileName}\r\n                  />\r\n                )}\r\n                {!isMarkdown && !isYaml && (\r\n                  <div style={{ padding: 24 }}>\r\n                    <textarea\r\n                      value={currentFile.content}\r\n                      onChange={(e) => openFile(currentFile.path, e.target.value)}\r\n                      style={{ width: '100%', height: 400, fontFamily: 'monospace' }}\r\n                    />\r\n                    <Button type=\"primary\" onClick={() => handleSave(currentFile.content)} style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>\r\n                      保存\r\n                    </Button>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                )}\r\n              </Card>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            {/* AI 工具栏（固定在底部） */}\r\n            <div style={{ marginTop: 16, flexShrink: 0 }}>\r\n              <Card title=\"AI 创作工具\">\r\n                <Space wrap>\r\n                  <Button\r\n                    type=\"primary\"\r\n                    icon={<ThunderboltOutlined />}\r\n                    onClick={handleSmartContinuation}\r\n                    loading={isGenerating}\r\n                  >\r\n                    智能续写\r\n                  </Button>\r\n                </Space>\r\n              </Card>\r\n\r\n              {/* AI 输出预览 */}\r\n              {(aiOutput || streamingContent) && (\r\n                <Card\r\n                  title=\"AI 输出预览\"\r\n                  style={{ marginTop: 16 }}\r\n                  extra={\r\n                    <Space>\r\n                      <Button\r\n                        icon={<CopyOutlined />}\r\n                        onClick={() => {\r\n                          navigator.clipboard.writeText(aiOutput || streamingContent)\r\n                          message.success('已复制')\r\n                        }}\r\n                      >\r\n                        复制\r\n                      </Button>\r\n                      <Button\r\n                        type=\"primary\"\r\n                        icon={<CheckOutlined />}\r\n                        onClick={handleApplyToEditor}\r\n                      >\r\n                        应用到编辑器\r\n                      </Button>\r\n                    </Space>\r\n                  }\r\n                >\r\n                  <div style={{ whiteSpace: 'pre-wrap', fontFamily: 'monospace', maxHeight: 300, overflow: 'auto' }}>\r\n                    {streamingContent || aiOutput}\r\n                    {isStreaming && <span style={{ animation: 'blink 1s infinite' }}>▌</span>}\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </Card>\r\n              )}\r\n            </div>\r\n          </>\r\n        ) : (\r\n          <div style={{ flex: 1, display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>\r\n            <div style={{ textAlign: 'center', color: '#888' }}>\r\n              <Title level={3}>创作工作台</Title>\r\n              <Text>从左侧大纲树选择一个文件开始编辑</Text>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        )}\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  )\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport default ChapterWorkspace\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775273959365}}
{"type":"message","id":"b7d66017","parentId":"80a291a5","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:39:26.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我检查一下是否问题在于初始渲染时的某些状态更新。让我看看是否有无限循环的风险。\n\n现在让我仔细看看整个 useEffect 部分，它负责初始化：\n\n```javascript\nuseEffect(() => {\n  if (propCurrentPath) {\n    console.log('[ChapterWorkspace] Initializing with path:', propCurrentPath)\n    const load = async () => {\n      try {\n        const charsDir = joinPath(propCurrentPath, 'characters')\n        const files = await window.electronAPI.readdir(charsDir)\n        // ...\n      } catch (e) {\n        // ...\n      }\n    }\n    load()\n  }\n}, [propCurrentPath])\n```\n\n这个代码看起来没有明显的无限循环问题。\n\n可能的问题：\n1. window.electronAPI.readdir 可能没有正确实现或者挂起\n2. 可能某些状态更新触发了连锁反应\n\n让我检查一下是否有任何关于这个问题的已知bug或者console错误。\n\n我应该直接查看问题并提供一个修复方案。基于我对代码的分析，最可能的原因是初始化时调用了可能挂起的 API。让我添加超时和错误处理来解决这个问题。\n\n让我先看看整个ChapterWorkspace的渲染逻辑，找出是什么导致了卡死。\n\n另一个可能的原因是：组件可能在 mounted 后尝试立即执行某个AI调用。让我查看一下这个组件中是否有任何自动触发的AI调用。\n\n\n在仔细检查后，我认为问题可能是初始化时对 window.electronAPI 的调用没有响应，这会无限期地挂起整个应用。我需要为这些 API 调用添加超时和错误处理来解决这个问题。\n\n现在我来生成一个修复版本。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1880ded619e948c0b5a839ee","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1,"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/ChapterWorkspace.tsx"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":79270,"output":380,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775273959372,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a0785963-8c4b-4a1c-84e6-8355c50abd6f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db1be9c0","parentId":"b7d66017","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:39:26.237Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1880ded619e948c0b5a839ee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import React, { useState, useCallback, useEffect } from 'react'\r\nimport { Button, Card, Typography, Space, message, Select, Divider } from 'antd'\r\nimport {\r\n  FileTextOutlined,\r\n  CopyOutlined,\r\n  CheckOutlined,\r\n  ThunderboltOutlined,\r\n  UserOutlined,\r\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\r\nimport * as aiService from '../services/aiService'\r\nimport { useWorkspaceStore } from '../stores/workspaceStore'\r\nimport { usePromptStore } from '../stores/promptStore'\r\nimport FileTree from './FileTree'\r\nimport MarkdownEditor from './MarkdownEditor'\r\nimport YAMLEditor from './YAMLEditor'\r\nimport { joinPath } from '../utils/pathUtils'\r\n\r\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\r\n\r\ninterface ChapterWorkspaceProps {\r\n  currentPath?: string\r\n  isProjectOpen?: boolean\r\n  onClose?: () => void\r\n}\r\n\r\nconst ChapterWorkspace: React.FC<ChapterWorkspaceProps> = ({\r\n  currentPath: propCurrentPath,\r\n  isProjectOpen = false,\r\n  onClose\r\n}) => {\r\n  const [characterList, setCharacterList] = useState<Array<{id: string, name: string, path: string}>>([])\r\n  const [loadingCharacters, setLoadingCharacters] = useState(false)\r\n  const [fileTreeRefreshKey, setFileTreeRefreshKey] = useState(0)\r\n\r\n  const {\r\n    currentFile,\r\n    aiOutput,\r\n    isGenerating,\r\n    streamingContent,\r\n    isStreaming,\r\n    currentCharacter,\r\n    openFile,\r\n    saveFile,\r\n    setAIOutput,\r\n    setStreamingContent,\r\n    setIsGenerating,\r\n    setIsStreaming,\r\n    setCurrentCharacter,\r\n  } = useWorkspaceStore()\r\n\r\n\n[316 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775273966233}}
{"type":"message","id":"dab7bf3f","parentId":"db1be9c0","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:40:03.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我仔细检查初始化部分并找出问题所在。我发现了问题 - 在ChapterWorkspace.tsx中有一些潜在的问题:\n\n1. 在 useEffect 中调用 window.electronAPI.readdir 可能会无限等待\n2. 没有超时控制\n\n让我编辑文件并添加超时和错误处理。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d56930dc4dbbc696727baef34f697","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"// 初始化 - 不依赖 loadCharacters 避免循环\n  useEffect(() => {\n    let mounted = true\n    if (propCurrentPath) {\n      console.log('[ChapterWorkspace] Initializing with path:', propCurrentPath)\n      const load = async () => {\n        try {\n          const charsDir = joinPath(propCurrentPath, 'characters')\n          // 添加超时保护，防止无限等待\n          const timeoutPromise = new Promise((_, reject) => \n            setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Timeout')), 5000)\n          )\n          const readdirPromise = window.electronAPI.readdir(charsDir)\n          const files = await Promise.race([readdirPromise, timeoutPromise]) as any[]\n          if (!mounted) return\n          if (files && files.length > 0) {\n            const chars = files\n              .filter((f: any) => f.name.endsWith('.yaml') || f.name.endsWith('.yml'))\n              .map((f: any) => ({\n                id: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n                name: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n                path: joinPath(charsDir, f.name)\n              }))\n            setCharacterList(chars)\n          }\n        } catch (e) {\n          if (!mounted) return\n          console.log('No characters directory found or failed to load:', e)\n          setCharacterList([])\n        }\n      }\n      load()\n    }\n    return () => { mounted = false }\n  }, [propCurrentPath])","oldText":"// 初始化 - 不依赖 loadCharacters 避免循环\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (propCurrentPath) {\n      console.log('[ChapterWorkspace] Initializing with path:', propCurrentPath)\n      const load = async () => {\n        try {\n          const charsDir = joinPath(propCurrentPath, 'characters')\n          const files = await window.electronAPI.readdir(charsDir)\n          if (files && files.length > 0) {\n            const chars = files\n              .filter((f: any) => f.name.endsWith('.yaml') || f.name.endsWith('.yml'))\n              .map((f: any) => ({\n                id: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n                name: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n                path: joinPath(charsDir, f.name)\n              }))\n            setCharacterList(chars)\n          }\n        } catch (e) {\n          console.log('No characters directory found or failed to load:', e)\n          setCharacterList([])\n        }\n      }\n      load()\n    }\n  }, [propCurrentPath])","path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/ChapterWorkspace.tsx"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2322,"output":675,"cacheRead":77696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775273966238,"responseId":"019d5692f4bccae704431dde4c0cf7e1"}}
