{"type":"message","id":"6cd3f26a","parentId":"ce197d93","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:40:34.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我检查一下是否还有其他可能导致挂起的地方，比如 FileTree 组件或其他地方。让我检查 App.tsx 中 workspace 的渲染，看看是否有任何其他问题。实际上，让我再看一下 App.tsx 中的 menu items 和相关代码，确定是否还有其他问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我已找到并修复了问题。\n\n## 🔍 问题原因\n\n**ChapterWorkspace.tsx** 初始化时调用 `window.electronAPI.readdir()` 读取 characters 目录，但：\n\n1. **API 调用没有超时** — 如果 electron 主进程没有响应，会无限期等待\n2. **缺少 mounted 状态检查** — 组件卸载后仍可能触发状态更新\n3. **loadCharacters 函数也有同样问题**\n\n## 🔧 修复内容\n\n**文件：** `/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/ChapterWorkspace.tsx`\n\n修复了两处 `readdir` 调用，添加了：\n\n```typescript\n// 1. 添加 5 秒超时保护\nconst timeoutPromise = new Promise((_, reject) => \n  setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Timeout')), 5000)\n)\nconst files = await Promise.race([readdirPromise, timeoutPromise])\n\n// 2. 添加组件卸载检查\nlet mounted = true\nreturn () => { mounted = false }\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 重新构建并测试\n\n在你的 Windows 电脑上运行：\n\n```cmd\ncd D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\\novel-desktop-app\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n然后点击\"创作工作台\"测试是否修复。\n\n---\n\n如果仍然卡死，请告诉我具体的错误信息，我可以继续排查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":11972,"output":333,"cacheRead":69376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775274012463,"responseId":"019d56932a49cd01c544af7378386ad2"}}
