{"type":"message","id":"2f1a4fa2","parentId":"24cbc3de","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:48:42.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All fixes are applied. Let me summarize for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## ✅ 自动化修复完成\n\n我做了以下修复来解决\"创作工作台\"卡死问题：\n\n---\n\n### 修复 1：懒加载 ChapterWorkspace\n**文件：** `src/renderer/src/App.tsx`\n\n```typescript\n// 之前：直接导入（立即加载）\nimport ChapterWorkspace from './components/ChapterWorkspace'\n\n// 现在：懒加载（点击时再加载）\nconst ChapterWorkspace = React.lazy(() => import('./components/ChapterWorkspace'))\n```\n\n### 修复 2：添加 Suspense 包装\n确保加载时显示 loading 状态，不会卡死\n\n### 修复 3：防御性空值检查\n**文件：** `src/renderer/src/components/ChapterWorkspace.tsx`\n\n添加了 `if (!propCurrentPath)` 防御检查，在没有打开项目时显示友好提示而不是卡死\n\n### 修复 4：之前的超时保护\n之前已添加 5 秒超时保护，防止 `readdir` 无限等待\n\n---\n\n## 📋 重新测试\n\n```cmd\ncd D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\\novel-desktop-app\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n1. 先打开一个项目\n2. 然后点击\"创作工作台\"\n\n应该不会再卡死了。如果还有问题请告诉我错误信息。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":88623,"output":271,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88894,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775274517742,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f040b8bf-db9f-4432-97c2-bff2ea31d1d2"}}
